{"title":"距离","authors":["邓万鹏"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"距离"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓万鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们面对面而坐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中间一张很旧的小桌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我突然感到有些晕眩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桌面上的木纹似乎在动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐地，成了一条内流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河河水流得很慢很慢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但把距离拉得很长很长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一边不住地用语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加固堤坝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边拚命吸烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在河面上制造出许多雾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此我无法看清你的面容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我的表和我的头脑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都累得不再想动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于用一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断了滔滔流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该分手了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——在梦中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"距离或许会缩短"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}